Free Trading Company V1.27
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This is a very old economic game my  brother  and  I  made  long  time  ago
(January  93). It is based on an old C64 classic called O.H.G. When we sold
it at that time, we gave away printed manuals, so  there  is  no  real  doc
file,  but I included the original Final Copy Document. This game is german
only, sorry guys.

Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~
The game should run on Kick 1.3 or higher. I recompiled  and  changed  some
music/sound  and  disk  io  code  to be uptodate, so it should run on every
processor from 68000 to 68060 (well, at least it runs on my 68060 ;) )

Shareware notice
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
F.T.C. is Shareware. Well, I guess this phrase  is  quite  senseless  as  I
never  got  one  penny  for  most  of  my  shareware  programs  (i.e Tubes,
StrikeCommander, MegaTron, Lemmings 2 Level Editor), unless I crippled them
down (AMCAF Extension). Nevertheless, try to enjoy the game.

History
~~~~~~~
V1.27: More internal changes. Fixed a severe AMOS bug.
V1.25: Internal changes: no need for math#?.library anymore.

